{"/service/ndnp/dlc/batch_dlc_pakula_ver02/data/sn84026749/00222254449/1927092401/0307.xml":{"full_text":"20\nLATEST NEWS AND QUOTATIONS OF THE FINANCIAL MARKETS\nk'4* 1 ;\u2014\u2014i a\u2014 4\nMOTORS LEAD\nSTOCK BALLI\n~r,\ns-;- B? tetersatleiial Newt Service\nNEW YORK, Sept. 24;\u2014Under\nthe leadship of General Motors, old\ndhd new stdck, Houston Oil and\na small number of the market\nspecialties, a sharp rally in prices\n.Wag sot in motion at the beginning\nof today's short sessions ,ot the\nstock market\nGeneral Motors jumped 5 points\nto gbove 269 fn the first period,\u2019 in\nresponse to rumors that the direc-\ntors at the November meeting 1\n\u25a0Would definitely place the new i\nstock on a |7 dividend basis, in\naddition to ordering an extra divi- t\ndend of |2 a share.\nBullish fdrces easily carried the\n-flay as the price of this recognised t\nleader was swept along in a con- j\nfldent wave of new buying.\nThe old stock reached 271 before\nthe end of the first first half\nhour in one of the most impres- t\ngive \u2018\u201cbullish demonstrations of the j\nweek.\nThe failure of any great volume\nof liquidation to reach the market\nin the last two days and the vir- i\ntual drying up of the source of t\nsupply of speculative stocks on a\ntelling price movfownt, was taken\nas an evidence of the surprising i\nstrength of the market at this\ntime. 4\nThe week-end'business review\u00ae\nwere colorless as far as the indica- J\ntions of the fall business revival\nwere concerned. j\nAnnouncement of the giant com-\nbination of Philadelphia and New\nNew York utility companies into 1\n1700,000,000 merger stimulated\nactive buying of the utility stocks, j\nConsolidated Gas resumed its\nspectacular forward move, while\nPhiladelphia Company and other\nwell known light and power stocks\nwere taken at the best level of j\nprices for the current movement. j\nAn enormous expansion in pub-\nlic. utility: 'service is now under\nway. J\nCHICAGO STOCKS I j\n(Furnished by W